metadata.name: THE PEARL OF THE MARMARA SEA IN THE MIST
metadata.description:
OSMANGAZI BRIDGE IS A SUSPENDED BRIDGE LOCATED ON THE IZMIT GULF OF THE SEA OF MARMARA. THE PHOTO I TAKEN WHEN THE SHIP WAS PASSING UNDER THE BRIDGE IN THE MIST. IN GENERAL, THIS REGION IS SUITABLE FOR FOG PHOTOGRAPHY IN AUTUMN AND SPRING WHEN THE SEASONAL CONDITIONS ARE APPROPRIATE. I WOULD LIKE TO PROVIDE THE PHOTO WHICH WON THE 2nd PRIZE IN THE NATIONAL COMPETITION. THIS WORK CAN BE YOURS.
